{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-05-29-06-52-import-ssm/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ohmybuck"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ff26a3da-f830-578f-b92c-18bc88cbe760","excerpt":"This gets any params in a  file for local use from SSM.","html":"<p>This gets any params in a <code class=\"language-text\">.env</code> file for local use from SSM.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/bash</span>\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">VAR_ENV_FILE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$1</span>\"</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">VAR_SSM_PREFIX</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$2</span>\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># To use:</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># sh import-ssm.sh &lt;VAR_ENV_FILE> &lt;SSM_PREFIX></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># EXAMPLE</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#   sh import-ssm.sh .env.example /application/project/environment/</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> -z <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"It appears you did not specify a file with the list of variables to fetch\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"sh import-ssm.sh .env.example /application/project/environment/\"</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> -z <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_SSM_PREFIX</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"It appears you did not specify an SSM prefix\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"sh import-ssm.sh .env.example /application/project/environment/\"</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>[STARTED IMPORT FROM SSM]\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">rm</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>.raw*\n<span class=\"token function\">rm</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>.local*\n\n<span class=\"token function\">grep</span> -v <span class=\"token string\">'^#'</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">read</span> LINE_ENV_VAR<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">UNPREFIXED_VAR</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $LINE_ENV_VAR <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"s/=.*//\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">VARIABLE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $UNPREFIXED_VAR <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">xargs</span> -I <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_SSM_PREFIX</span>{}\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">VALUE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $LINE_ENV_VAR <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"s/.*=//\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">LOOP_PARAM</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>aws ssm get-parameter --name <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VARIABLE</span>\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">LOOP_VALUE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $LOOP_PARAM <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> jq -r <span class=\"token string\">\".Parameter | .Value\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/\"/<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\\\\">\\\\</span><span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span>/g'</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VARIABLE</span>=<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">$LOOP_VALUE</span><span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>.raw\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$UNPREFIXED_VAR</span>=<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">$LOOP_VALUE</span><span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>.local\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[IMPORTED]: <span class=\"token variable\">$VARIABLE</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[SSM FAILED TO ADD]: <span class=\"token variable\">$VARIABLE</span>\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">done</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>[COMPLETED IMPORT FROM SSM]\"</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Import SSM","date":"May 29, 2020","description":"Import SSM"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-05-29-06-52-import-ssm/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-05-23-14-48-env-file-checker/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Env File Checker","draft":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-06-06-16-09-reduce-usage-of-reduce/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Reduce Usage Of Reduce","draft":null}}}}}